# NHL Project

This repository contains Jupyter notebooks with debugging exercises related to machine learning and data analysis for an NHL University project.

## Prerequisites

- Python 3.6 or higher
- pip (Python package installer)

## Setup Instructions

### Creating and Activating a Virtual Environment

#### Windows/macOS/Linux

```bash

# windows

# Navigate to the project directory
cd D:\python_projects\NHL Project

# Create a virtual environment
python -m venv venv

# Activate the virtual environment
venv\Scripts\activate

#macOS/Linux

# Navigate to the project directory
cd /path/to/NHL Project

# Create a virtual environment
python3 -m venv venv

# Activate the virtual environment
source venv/bin/activate

# Install dependencies from requirements.txt
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Finally use venv as Jupyter kernel